The paper deals with channel estimation for mmWave communication in massive MU-MIMO systems, which involves signal processing, communication theory, and hardware design. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the fundamental limits of communication and information processing. The paper also involves aspects of computer architecture and embedded systems, which are covered by cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) and cs.ET (Embedded Systems). The paper also involves control theory and optimization, which are covered by cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture).
